## User-invocable
When the user types `/sales-retro`, run this skill.

## Arguments
- `/sales-retro` тАФ last 7 days (default)
- `/sales-retro 14d` тАФ last 14 days
- `/sales-retro 30d` тАФ last 30 days

## Output contract

This skill emits **TWO Discord-sized code blocks** in one response:

1. **Message 1 тАФ Users** (signups, activation, quota, churn, big fish тАФ sourced from PostHog)
2. **Message 2 тАФ Sales Team** (meetings, customer calls, transcript-derived insights тАФ sourced from the Supabase MCP `pzhjwclpluxbfopctyot`)

Each message MUST be under 1950 characters. Cut content to fit; never split a section across messages.

